<div class="header-container">
<div class="header-title">
<h2>Receiving Startup Events In Single Instance Mode</h2>
</div>
<div class="header-nav">
<div class="nav-wrapper">
<a title="key: j" href="../splash/splash.html" class="nav-left"></a>
</div>
<div class="nav-wrapper">
